# Supabase local/runtime artifacts — never commit
.branches
.temp
.env

# ── DATA & SECRETS: MUST NEVER BE COMMITTED ──────────────────────────────
# The migrations/ folder is for SCHEMA-ONLY SQL (DDL). Never check in
# production data: users have bcrypt password hashes + emails, and the
# business tables hold customer prices / margins. Those belong in encrypted
# backups, not in git.
#
# Any of these filename patterns are blocked as a safety net:
seed_snapshot.sql
*_data.sql
*_data-only.sql
*.dump
*.backup
*.csv
data-*.sql
